"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The deal being discussed would involve a 60-day ceasefire extension, during which the Strait of Hormuz would be reopened, according to US media.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ceasefire Extension\",            \"translated_version\": \"El acuerdo que se discute incluir\u00eda una extensi\u00f3n de 60 d\u00edas de alto el fuego, durante la cual se reabrir\u00eda el Estrecho de Hormuz, seg\u00fan medios de EE.UU.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Extensi\u00f3n de Alto el Fuego\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Russia has confirmed that the Oreshnik missile, which reportedly travels over 10 times the speed of sound, was used.\",            \"english_title\": \"Oreshnik Missile Used\",            \"translated_version\": \"Rusia ha confirmado que se us\u00f3 el misil Oreshnik, que viaja m\u00e1s de 10 veces la velocidad del sonido.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Uso del Misil Oreshnik\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Officials say a suspect approached a checkpoint near a building and opened fire, wounding a bystander.\",            \"english_title\": \"Shooting at Checkpoint\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los oficiales dicen que un sospechoso se acerc\u00f3 a un control cerca de un edificio y dispar\u00f3, hiriendo a una persona.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Disparo en el Control\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"At least 82 people have died after a gas explosion at the Liushenyu mine in China.\",            \"english_title\": \"Gas Explosion in China\",            \"translated_version\": \"Al menos 82 personas han muerto despu\u00e9s de una explosi\u00f3n de gas en la mina Liushenyu en China.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Explosi\u00f3n de Gas en China\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Security forces faced resistance while trying to clear highway barriers during unrest over the government's economic policies.\",            \"english_title\": \"Highway Barriers Resistance\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las fuerzas de seguridad enfrentaron resistencia al intentar quitar barreras en la carretera durante disturbios por las pol\u00edticas econ\u00f3micas del gobierno.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Resistencia en la Carretera\"        }    ]}"